data.description: Ideal location and best layout available in Valley Ranch! This 4 bedroom/3 bath plus office is on a quiet street near the community entrance and backs up to a green belt. Walk just 2 short blocks to Kallison Elementary school or the gorgeous 10,000 sq ft amenities center. Enjoy a bright open layout with high ceilings, durable wood-look LVT flooring in the common areas and a large island kitchen with plenty of cabinets, granite counters, gas cooking and a walk-in pantry. The primary bedroom suite, office, 2 secondary bedrooms and another full bathroom are on the main level. A huge loft game room and guest suite with full bath complete the second level. All bedrooms have walk-in closets. The home is nearly new, built in 2020, and well cared for. Upgrades include an extended concrete patio for wonderful outdoor entertaining space, solar panels, water softener and epoxy floor with an Electric Vehicle charging station in the 2 car garage. Community amenities include a 2 acre fishing pond, 2 huge pools, water slides, water playground, party pavilion, basketball courts, tennis courts & children's playground. The clubhouse has a full gym, community room and on-site management office. **Special Financing  Incentives available on this property from SIRVA Mortgage.  ***************Open House Saturday, Feb. 17, 2:00-4:00pm******************
